Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:40.31,Title,,0,0,0,,Otani's Catastrophic Declaration!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-chan received her acceptance notice from the undergraduate university in Hokkaido,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...and she's been even more lovey-dovey with Nakao-chi than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani, who wants to become a teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...has started attending prep classes,\N and is studying for the entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.37,0:02:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like studying or taking tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I've decided to try for a technical college.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do about the next Umibouzu concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna pass this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Umibouzu we're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the last Umibouzu concert of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! But I don't really have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.46,0:02:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only time I have to study for exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was choking back tears when I finally decided not to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Who was it who said she was going to support me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Exam students sure have it hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mocking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If not, stop talking to me while I'm trying to memorize English vocabulary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet. Why are you following me, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to put it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a reason for coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's at the restaurant opposite your prep school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you working all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This way I can at least walk you halfway home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ribbon isn't on straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And your nails are too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please cut them before you come tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And tie your hair up tighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohori-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're five minutes late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the second day in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was held back at school by my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you to call ahead if that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:46.67,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another part-timer? What a cute boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,An Umibouzu wristband!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's the limited edition one that you can only get at his concerts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:03:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're a huge Umibouzu fan too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A mega fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awesome to have another Umibouzu fan around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! I'm feeling all excited now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san! Kohori-kun! Stop that right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,These dumplings are just delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. You made them, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's this younger co-worker of yours like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kohori-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,His face is kind of cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...and he's about as tall as Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your midget fetish speaking to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's got a midget fetish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Otani-kun seems to be working really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Otani-kun is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he stayed behind yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...and was asking the teacher lots of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:05:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani really is trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said. If I put my mind to it, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, getting into college won't be impossible for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In comparison, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...I need to decide what I'm going to do with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should just start doing this full time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorr—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't always make such a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:42.06,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Man... I really can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:44.53,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I was thinking of doing this full time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it needs more salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was too sweet, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get this part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this formula...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's up with all of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you're all ready to fly off into the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Risa, you're here? Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should add yams to the recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, you're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll definitely become a great artisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow... somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...I feel like I'm being left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My face looks terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get yelled at again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She said "Welcome."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you come here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying "What did you come here for" to your customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? Did you come here just to laugh at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This employee's attitude is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me know what you would like to order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At least me finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,P-P-Please go ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that hurt, you idiot!\NI'm a customer, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to prep class in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They even hold them on Sundays?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no weekends for exam students.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially not for the ones with bad grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly, exact—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Enough, enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Say Risa, where's that cute guy you mentioned last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not working today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:08:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kohori-kun? Doesn't look like he's here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Midget fetishist Risa's next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Midget fetishist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What? So that guy is short too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That's not important!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a huge Umibouzu fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get yelled at if I keep talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, my order...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well... She seems a lot happier than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you came to laugh at her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you were actually worried about her, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she was down about always getting chewed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,An exam student's got no time to worry about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're like that, Risa will hook up with that cute short kid behind your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:08:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So Otani has class on Sundays too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya, Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning to go out with him next Sunday since I'll have the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well. He's an exam student. It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:25.21,Superscript,,0,0,0,,GLOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this odd, gloomy atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, idiot. Don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, over here, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard he did terribly in the practice exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The results for his top choice school were all C's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I even sacrificed sleep for study...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even if you start studying now, you can't expect your grades to go up right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You've still got time, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll wear yourself out at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What the... You're just crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop blurting out whatever comes into your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Do what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've done that without you telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?\NAm I getting in his way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he's under a lot of stress, but couldn't he have been a little nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kohori-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! We're on together again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that? What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I cut myself just now when I was sharpening the knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what to do about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I break glasses and cut my hands all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I've had to use the first aid kit a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Old lady Matsumara helped me at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I kept getting hurt, so she told me I should deal with it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll get angry if she hears you calling her an old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! She's not here, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty funny, Koizumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really funny and kind.\NYou're a great person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been working here for six months, but this is the first time I've met someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in the kitchen, you're famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We can alway hear you shouting from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, "Whoops!" or, "I'm so sorry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I get yelled at by old lady Matsumara for shouting loudly like that too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. I called her "old lady" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Man! She's definitely not around, right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so funny! My stomach hurts from laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm feeling better now, at any rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather forecast was right.\NI was right to bring my umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've still got time, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This way I can at least walk you halfway home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She... probably didn't bring an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumara-san, is everything on our menu available to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't memorize the entire menu tonight, I'm not letting you go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there sure is a lot of text... I'm getting sleepy just looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You make mistakes because you don't know the menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've memorized all of the noodle dishes perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you have. We only have two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. So all of these menu items can also be to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should get something for Otani to have for dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped. Can't be helped. Can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san? Why are you sleeping here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If I bring him dinner, Otani will probably be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That was, uhh... S-S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I w-wasn't... th-that... uh... th-this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't kissing you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think, Otani. Please listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was who Nobu-chan was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Midget fetishist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm studying. Please be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:15:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She cheated on me with that midget she works with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, you got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it clearly. He definitely kissed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you only wanted me for my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't matter who it is, as long as he's short?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would deliberately look for a boyfriend shorter then herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so uncool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncool? You're calling me uncool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how busy Otani was with his exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you would two-time him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you were like, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you just listen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, there's absolutely nothing going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you say, but he went and did something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what he thinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, even if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:16:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:16:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'd already finished work...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I'd stayed to chat, I would've been yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Honestly, I'm not two-timing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell that shorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time he tries to lay a hand on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll give him a hook so hard his nose will be crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you shouldn't punch him in the nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious. I'll really do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've hit him when I had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing him this upset over me makes me kind of happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no laughing matter, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a moment of weakness, and by the time I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was your boyfriend, right? I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohori-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. I was asleep anyway, so I don't remember a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you busy this Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an Umibouzu event.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Umibouzu... Umibouzu... Umibouzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What kind of event?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a radio event. Only fifty people get to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! And you won?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! And I'd like to invite you. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just this once...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd really like to go with you, Koizumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do anything that will make trouble for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:19:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I go? Taking everything into consideration it's obvious that I shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm not interested in him, going to a concert with him after what happened is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no excuse this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! No way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So... it's a "no," then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, yay, yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the world's biggest idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say no to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not cheating. We're just going to a concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hurry there and then hurry on home once it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you, baby!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}See you again at Osaka Castle Hall next year!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay. That ends our broadcast of the Umibouzu concert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She was at work, so she'll definitely be happy when I give this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an invite-only concert, after all. A once in a lifetime thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my first time seeing Umibouzu perform before such a small audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for inviting me to such a great event.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I finally asked you out. I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I... towards you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh! I'm asking you what you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who pressured her into going to the Umibouzu concert with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohori-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So the two of you went to a concert together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that. I was the one who really wanted to go to the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's in the wrong, so if you really want to break someone's nose, break mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.28,0:21:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm breaking up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go out with someone like you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say you're going to break up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you want with that midget, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "midget"? He's taller than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: Many Future Paths!! The Circumstances We All Bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.80,0:23:39.57,Preview Title,,0,0,0,,Many Future Paths!!\N The Circumstances We All Bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
